title: DeAndre Jordan hilariously attempted his best CP3 impersonation in warmups
text:
Chris Paul and DeAndre Jordan had a fun game of HORSE before their game on Monday night.
Follow the leader.
A post shared by LA Clippers (@laclippers) on Mar 6, 2017 at 7:45pm PST
Gotta give props to the big man here. CP3 didn’t make this easy on him and Jordan made a heck of a recovery to keep up with the handles.
At first it looked like things weren’t going too well.
But he ended up doing just fine!
There had to be a second part of this we didn’t see. Hopefully on DeAndre’s turn he blocked a big man trying to dunk in the lane and Chris Paul had to match it. This was a night of mimicking for the Clippers in general. Later in the night Jamal Crawford did his best Blake Griffin impersonation .
